{"tid":2313430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一田沙田及觀塘員工初步確診！星期日暫停營業","createTime":"2020-12-05T18:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T05:07:45.000Z","uid":5195,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0385b9445cc2b98614018fdad70296356901f295","tid":2313430,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T18:31:49.000Z","msg":"一田沙田/觀塘店6/12休息<br />\n<br />\n接獲通知，沙田店家品部一田員工（非品牌專櫃推廣員），以及觀塘店壽司專櫃員工初步確診新冠肺炎，為安全起見，沙田及觀塘店6/12將暫停營業，由專業清潔公司進行全店深度清潔；同時，已安排沙田及觀塘店所有員工作快速核酸檢測，待確認檢測結果陰性才准予復工，重開日期另行通知。不便之處，敬請見諒。<br />\n<br />\n沙田員工3-4/12休假，5/12 上班後不適回家休息，檢測後初步確診，工作期間有帶囗罩。觀塘店壽司專櫃員工，除星期四3/12早上上班外，由30/11-5/12休假，工作期間有帶口罩、手套等裝備。"},{"pid":"6564d1913aecbecfda49ea7c5fa6346b03918be5","tid":2313430,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T18:32:43.000Z","msg":"仲要停正星期日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0322e8e4052a7a5761111f53341f2bd4e60c187d","tid":2313430,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T18:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5bcbe171e5935a4f785ba4c48946f47bfc8282","tid":2313430,"uid":194781,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T18:39:28.000Z","msg":"前一排一田先特賣日 人山人海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43252c6fa6b9d287549d30c3b0d032b487aaa715","tid":2313430,"uid":41873,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T18:44:07.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">武漢肺炎</span></span>"},{"pid":"0b8b86b55efb2df08bd807d1586c40a281cb3610","tid":2313430,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bf5bcbe171e5935a4f785ba4c48946f47bfc8282","tid":2313430,"uid":194781,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T18:39:28.000Z","msg":"前一排一田先特賣日 人山人海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyT